'''SandForce'''是一家美国[[無廠半導體公司|無廠半導體公司]]，坐落于[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[米尔皮塔斯_(加利福尼亚州)|米尔皮塔斯]]，业务为设计和制造用于[[固态硬盘|固态硬盘]]（SSD）的[[闪存控制器|闪存控制器]]。<ref name="Trendfocus">{{cite web|url=http://www.sandforce.com/userfiles/file/downloads/SandForce_Profile_TrendFocus.pdf|title=SandForce Emerges to Reshape SSD Landscape|accessdate=2010-08-31|last=Geenen|first=Mark|publisher=TRENDFOCUS, Inc|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716003203/http://www.sandforce.com/userfiles/file/downloads/SandForce_Profile_TrendFocus.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年1月4日，SandForce被[[LSI公司|LSI公司]]收购，成为LSI的闪存组件部门。在LSI之后，2014年5月6日被[[博通有限|安华高科技]]收购<ref name="avagocomplete">{{cite web|url=https://finance.yahoo.com/news/avago-technologies-completes-acquisition-lsi-133032023.html|title=Avago Technologies Completes Acquisition of LSI Corporation|accessdate=2014-06-08|publisher=Yahoo! Finance|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714224054/http://finance.yahoo.com/news/avago-technologies-completes-acquisition-lsi-133032023.html|archivedate=2014-07-14}}</ref>，同月29日，希捷科技宣布有意收购LSI的闪存组件部门。<ref name="sgpurchase">{{cite web|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20140529005611/en/Seagate-Acquire-LSI%E2%80%99s-Flash-Businesses-Avago|title=Seagate Acquires SandForce from LSI/Avago|accessdate=2014-06-08|last=Vättö|first=Kristian|publisher=AnandTech|archive-date=2014-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140601031745/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20140529005611/en/Seagate-Acquire-LSI%E2%80%99s-Flash-Businesses-Avago|dead-url=no}}</ref>

SandForce由Alex Naqvi和Rado Danilak于2006年成立。2009年4月，他们宣布进入固态驱动器市场。<ref name="Bagley">{{cite web|url=http://www.sandforce.com/userfiles/file/downloads/SandForce_Snapshot_SSG-Now.pdf|title=SandForce Enterprise Solid State Drive Processor with DuraClass Technology|accessdate=2010-08-31|last=Bagley|first=James|publisher=StorageStrategiesNow|archive-date=2011-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716003247/http://www.sandforce.com/userfiles/file/downloads/SandForce_Snapshot_SSG-Now.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Merritt">{{cite web|url=http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4082693/Startup-brings-MLC-to-server-flash-drives|title=Startup brings MLC to server flash drives|accessdate=2010-08-31|last=Merritt|first=Rick|publisher=EETimes|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101030171914/http://www.eetimes.com/electronics-news/4082693/Startup-brings-MLC-to-server-flash-drives|archive-date=2010-10-30|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

SandForce不销售完整的固态驱动器，而是销售被称为“SSD处理器”的[[闪存控制器|闪存控制器]]给合作伙伴，然后由制造商为公司和最终用户打造和销售完整的SSD。<ref name="Peters">{{cite web|url=http://www.sandforce.com/userfiles/file/downloads/SandForce_Profile_ESG_Apr09.pdf|title=SandForce--Forcing a Solid State Reconsideration|accessdate=2010-08-31|last=Peters|first=Mark|publisher=Enterprise Strategy Group|archive-date=2010-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100922195422/http://www.sandforce.com/userfiles/file/downloads/SandForce_Profile_ESG_Apr09.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过，LSI的另一个部门在LSI Nytro PCIe产品线中有使用SandForce SSD处理器。SSD市场分析师和StorageSearch.com的发行者Zsolt Kerekes在2011年表示，SandForce是最知名的SSD控制器制造商。<ref name="ss">{{cite web|url=http://www.storagesearch.com/sandforce.html|title=SandForce - circa 2011|accessdate=2013-05-20|work=StorageSearch.com web site|archive-date=2013-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130420071918/http://www.storagesearch.com/sandforce.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 历史 ==
