othardware.com/news/kingston-hyperx-predator-pci-express-ssd-unveiled--with-lsi-sandforce-sf3700-flash-controller |archive-date=2016-05-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>{{tsl|en|Mushkin}}也在消費電子展上展示了使用SF 3700系列的产品，推出他们高达480GB（512GiB）的[[M.2|M.2]] Helix系列，并在2.5英寸款式内最多2TB。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/7660/mushkin-ces-2014-sf3700-ssds |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104074846/http://www.anandtech.com/show/7660/mushkin-ces-2014-sf3700-ssds |dead-url=no }}</ref>

