== 问题 ==
第一代SandForce控制器不完全符合SATA规范<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hardocp.com/article/2013/06/03/asus_z87a_lga_1150_motherboard_review/7#.Uq4DGZDU6Cy |title=ASUS Z87-A LGA 1150 Motherboard Review/Conclusion |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202034510/http://www.hardocp.com/article/2013/06/03/asus_z87a_lga_1150_motherboard_review/7#.Uq4DGZDU6Cy |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并且与Intel [[Haswell|Haswell]]平台不兼容。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ocztechnologyforum.com/forum/showthread.php?111964-Vertex-2-Agility-2-and-Haswell |title=Vertex 2 - Agility 2 and Haswell |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2013-08-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130809194602/http://www.ocztechnologyforum.com/forum/showthread.php?111964-Vertex-2-Agility-2-and-Haswell |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://forum.corsair.com/v3/showthread.php?t=122058 |title=Force F80 not compatible with Haswell? |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2017-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202173213/http://forum.corsair.com/v3/showthread.php?t=122058 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在引入SF-2000系列控制器后，一些使用该驱动器的用户报告遇到如[[蓝屏死机|蓝屏死机]]或冻结问题。2011年6月初，[[Corsair|Corsair Memory]]对特定序列号的120 GB Force 3发出召回，但这没有召回其他使用SandForce SF-2000控制器的Force 3驱动器，因此该召回似乎与控制器无关。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://forum.corsair.com/v3/showthread.php?t=95825|title=Corsair Force Series 3 SSD Issue Resolution: Drive Return Procedure|accessdate=2011-08-24|date=2011-06-07|publisher=Corsair|archive-date=2011-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110902143301/http://forum.corsair.com/v3/showthread.php?t=95825|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年10月，SandForce通过其制造合作伙伴（诸如[[OCZ|OCZ]]）发送固件更新，修复了报告的问题<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.anandtech.com/show/4973/sandforce-identifies-firmware-bug-causing-bsod-issue-fix-available-today|title=SandForce Identifies Firmware Bug Causing BSOD Issue, Fix Available Today|accessdate=2012-04-16|date=2011-10-17|publisher=Anandtech.com|archive-date=2012-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120422215338/http://www.anandtech.com/show/4973/sandforce-identifies-firmware-bug-causing-bsod-issue-fix-available-today|dead-url=no}}</ref>2012年8月，一个名为Tweaktown的网站发现使用5.0.1和5.0.2版本固件的基于SandForce的SSD存在的问题，其中的TRIM支持在完全擦除SSD时没有执行优化，但也确认5.0.3和5.0.4版本的固件已解决该问题。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tweaktown.com/articles/4870/lsi_sandforce_5_series_ssd_firmware_trim_lost_and_found_performance_investigated/index.html|title=LSI SandForce 5 Series SSD Firmware - TRIM Lost and Found, Performance Investigated|accessdate=2012-09-10|date=2012-08-01|publisher=TweakTown.com|archive-date=2012-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005134431/http://www.tweaktown.com/articles/4870/lsi_sandforce_5_series_ssd_firmware_trim_lost_and_found_performance_investigated/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2012年，SandForce基于SF-2000的驱动器被发现只包含AES-128加密，而不是宣称的AES-256加密。有推测认为，较低等级的加密是为取得美国ITAR许可证资格，该许可证排除将提供特定加密级别功能的产品销往被选定的与美国有矛盾或明显不友好的国家。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.storagereview.com/lsi_sandforce_aes_encryption_strength_flaw_revealed |title=LSI SandForce AES Encryption Strength Flaw Revealed |access-date=2017-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170201012744/http://www.storagereview.com/lsi_sandforce_aes_encryption_strength_flaw_revealed |archive-date=2017-02-01 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bit-tech.net/news/hardware/2012/06/12/sandforce-sf-2000-encryption/1 |title=SandForce SF-2000 encryption flaw discovered |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2017-01-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170131231315/http://www.bit-tech.net/news/hardware/2012/06/12/sandforce-sf-2000-encryption/1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>诸如[[金士顿|金士顿]] SSDNow V+200和KC100等产品修订了其文档，标明使用128位AES加密。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ocdrift.com/kingston-technology-statement-on-lsi-sandforce-sf-2000-encryption-flaw/ |title=Kingston Technology statement on LSI SandForce SF-2000 encryption flaw |access-date=2017-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170202020035/http://www.ocdrift.com/kingston-technology-statement-on-lsi-sandforce-sf-2000-encryption-flaw/ |archive-date=2017-02-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>英特尔为受影响的英特尔520系列固态硬盘用户提供退款，截止时间2012年10月1日。而金士顿提供交换计划，为要求替换的用户支付运费。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://techreport.com/news/23096/256-bit-aes-encryption-broken-in-sandforce-ssd-controllers |title=256-bit AES encryption broken in SandForce SSD controllers |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2017-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170123141407/http://techreport.com/news/23096/256-bit-aes-encryption-broken-in-sandforce-ssd-controllers |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 营销计划 ==
2010年5月，SandForce引入“SandForce驱动”计划。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.storagesearch.com/ssd-history-2010-q2.html|title=SSD Market Milestones - 2010 2nd quarter|accessdate=2013-05-20|author=Zsolt Kerekes|publisher=StorageSearch.com|archive-date=2013-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816103225/http://www.storagesearch.com/ssd-history-2010-q2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>“Intel Inside”计划与BASF广告口号说：“我们不制造你使用的东西，我们让你使用更好的东西”是类似的宣传，公司宣传最终产品中的一个组件。SandForce创建了一个合作伙伴可以在SSD上或其广告上展示的标志，以表明其内部采用SandForce控制器和SandForce编写的固件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100518005620/en/SandForce-Driven-SSDs-Establish-Era-Performance-Reliability|title="SandForce Driven" SSDs Establish New Era of Performance and Reliability|accessdate=2010-08-31|publisher=BusinessWire|archive-date=2010-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008145413/http://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20100518005620/en/SandForce-Driven-SSDs-Establish-Era-Performance-Reliability|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lsi.com/partners/SandForce-Driven-Program/Pages/default.aspx|title=SandForce Driven Members|accessdate=2012-11-30|publisher=lsi.com|archive-date=2012-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121118040327/http://www.lsi.com/partners/SandForce-Driven-Program/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2013年10月，SandForce驱动计划有38名成员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lsi.com/partners/sandforce-driven-program/pages/default.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-01-25 |archive-date=2014-08-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819210623/http://www.lsi.com/partners/SandForce-Driven-Program/Pages/default.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

SandForce于2011年1月创建了“SandForce可信”计划，该计划确定了提供与SandForce SSD处理器兼容的设备、工具和服务的批准供应商。它是一种{{tsl|en|Approved vendor list|获批准供应商列表}}，帮助SSD OEM厂商和制造商得到更高水平的服务与支持。

